s.text: It is also possible that my general grouchiness on the subject of the Internet has to do with the fact that I've expended a lot of energy these past few years claiming that the valuations of Internet stocks make no sense, and that, in general, what I've come to think of as the Internet stock market--people using the Internet to "learn" about Internet stocks, when they then trade via an Internet site--is insane.
